710286f-b.text:
Eighth Avenue, north from W. 145th Street, as photographed from
the express platform of the Ninth Avenue "El."
View 1 shows details of same and buildings at the N. W. (left)
and N. E. (right) corners of 145th Street.
View 2 is from the other extremity and includes buildings at
the four corners of 146th Street.
June 5, 1940
Views 1,2
P. L. Sperr
